%h1
  Sign up
  
#login-main
  %h2
    Create your Gifty Fifty account, it’s free!
  %p
    Once you’ve made it, will be easier to make contributions to your friends or create your events with the gift you really want.
  %p
    = link_to(image_tag('connect_facebook.png'), '/auth/facebook')
    = link_to(image_tag('connect_twitter.png'), '/auth/twitter')
    
  = form_for(resource, :as => resource_name, :url => registration_path(resource_name)) do |f| 
    = devise_error_messages! 
    
    %p
      = f.label :first_name 
      = f.text_field :first_name
    %p
      = f.label :email 
      = f.text_field :email 

    %p
      = f.label :password 
      = f.password_field :password 

    %p
      = f.label :password_confirmation 
      = f.password_field :password_confirmation 

    %p
      = f.submit "Sign up" 

#login-aside
  %h2
    What is Gifty Fifty?
  %p
    A service where your friends and family contribuite with a part of the total cost of your gift.
  %p
    We help you to get the gift you want and your friends won't waste money on useless things you don't like.
  .explination-box
    = image_tag 'gift_home.png'
    %p
      %span
        1. Choose your gift
      %br
      Find your gift on the internet, then copy-paste the URL in our home page and edit your event.
  .explination-box
    = image_tag 'megaphone_home.png'
    %p
      %span
        2. Spread the word
      %br
      Invite your friends through your social networks to start making contributions to your gift.
  .explination-box
    = image_tag 'machine_home.png'
    %p
      %span
        3. Get it!
      %br
      Once you've reached your money goal thanks all your friends' contributions, you can buy it.
.clearBoth